content:
Not sure where else to put this. I've convinced Trump supporters to not vote this year, and independents to vote Kamala-Walz, with emphasis on Trump's habit of hurting people, including his own supporters, based on his changing impulses. I provide some key examples every time. Attached is the script I've used when doing calls on my own (prior to joining here).

I have a longer version too, but this hits the main points
Great job, Jay! Thanks so much for your hard work and insights!
If you click on it then right click and open the link, it'll open in your browser in readable size. there's some good points in there!
